oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Public square shops
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the public square in Columbia showing businesses including National Stores, Sterling Cafe, Capitol Billiards, and Derryberry Dependable Drugs. There are four cars parked by meters, center and left. A label at the bottom right of the photograph reads "December 1961."
